  "time_ut": 1658920449,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd6 \u0d85\u0dba \u0dc4\u0db3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Those who set fire to the President's house have been identified",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Criminal Investigation Department seeks the public's assistance in establishing the identity of 14 key operatives who have been identified in connection with the incident of trespassing into President Ranil Wickramasinghe's house at Fifth Lane, Colombo 03, attacking and setting fire to the property.",
        "The police headquarters had released the photos of these 14 people to the media today to identify the right criminals in the incident and take necessary legal measures.",
        "The Criminal Investigation Department has started investigations regarding this incident, and the police headquarters said that they want to confirm the identity of these key actors from the close-up video footage related to the incident.",
        "In support of the struggle, the activists who came to Colombo from all over the island on the 9th, after relinquishing their grip on the Presidential Palace, the Presidential Secretariat, the Prime Minister's offices, another group forcibly broke into the President's private residence at night and damaged and destroyed its properties.",
        "According to police sources, the destroyed properties include the library, antiques and paintings that had been maintained in the President's residence for several years.",
        "After this incident, the investigation of the incident has been handed over to the Criminal Investigation Department.",
        "Several suspects were previously arrested in connection with this incident and remanded.",
        "The Criminal Investigation Department requests the public to inform the public through WhatsApp or calls on the numbers 0718594950, 0718594929, 0112422176, if they have any information regarding the persons in these photos released by the police to the media."
      ],
